abstract: Gunmen believed to be Palestinians fire more than 20 bullets at Israeli car in drive-by shooting in occupied West Bank, wounding Israeli couple; Palestinian stabs and wounds two Israelis in Hebron before being fatally shot.
lead_paragraph: Gunmen presumed to be Palestinians fired more than 20 bullets at an Israeli car in a drive-by shooting.

headline.print_headline: Middle East; West Bank: Attackers Wound 4 Israelis

snippet: Gunmen presumed to be Palestinians fired more than 20 bullets at an Israeli car in a drive-by shooting.
